        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/378/472",
        "text": [
          "۳۷۸. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): الْبُخْلُ جَامعٌ لِمَسَاوِئِ الْعُيُوبِ، وَهُوَ زِمَامٌ يُقَادُ بِهِ إِلَى كُلِّ سُوءٍ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
            "378. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Miserliness contains all other evil vices and is the rein with which one can be led to every evil."
          ]
        }
      }
